Hello Raffaella,
I trust this email finds you well.
Following on from email last Monday - I would like to receive your permissi=
on to begin the process of obtaining preliminary tender responses for your =
claim.
It would be a significant progression if I could work with tender responden=
ts and begin the tendering process before the beginning of the Christmas br=
eak.
Please advise me if I have your permission to begin this process.
Many Thanks,
Grant.


