Good morning Raffaella, Richard & All,
Please find attached the following documents for your review:

  *   Combustion pre-decontamination survey [ sent prior ]
  *   ANZ1789 supplementary report
  *   Post fire structural assessment report
  *   ANZ1789 scope of works [ revised & updated ]
The updated scope-of-works attached has been created as a proposed inclusiv=
e response to the findings of all the documents attached.
While you are reviewing the attachments, I would like to propose that I beg=
in the process of obtaining repair proposals from Tower approved builders t=
o progress the claim as quickly as possible.
If I send out the scope of works now and offer to meet with the tender resp=
ondents onsite, we may well have some preliminary costings to hand prior to=
 the end of the business year.
Please confirm your approval for me to begin the process of preliminary pri=
cing now.
Best Regards,
Grant.


