<b>Cc:</b> Lance O'Riley &lt;Lance.ORiley@tower.co.nz&gt;; Bryan Strong &lt=
;Bryan.Strong@tower.co.nz&gt;; Kelly Mason &lt;Kelly.Mason@tower.co.nz&gt;;=
 Arna Neems &lt;Arna.Neems@tower.co.nz&gt;<br>
<b>Subject:</b> FW: C90306048 - Fire at 23 Mays Street, Devonport [WW-ACTIV=
E.FID3167762]<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
