<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:1.0pt;color:white">Kia ora =
Grant, Thank you for your email and for confirming receipt of our letter. F=
riday, 17 October after 2:</span><span style=3D"font-size:1.0pt;font-family=
:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:white">=E2=80=8A</span><span style=3D"f=
ont-size:1.0pt;color:white">00
 pm works for me, and I=E2=80=99d appreciate it if testing and assessment c=
ould be scheduled accordingly. I also reserve my right to undertake</span><=
o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:1.0pt;color:white">&nbsp;</=
span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Kia ora Grant,<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Thank you for your email and for confirming receipt =
of our letter.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Friday, 17 October after 2:00 pm works for me, and I=
=E2=80=99d appreciate it if testing and assessment could be scheduled accor=
dingly.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I also reserve my right to undertake independent tes=
ting and assessment of the property to ensure a full and impartial evaluati=
on.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Having reviewed the proposed plan, I=E2=80=99m conce=
rned the current testing schedule appears incomplete. It does not include t=
he first floor, roof cavity, or the large upper deck, and the basement cove=
rage seems partial, given the known extent
 of smoke, water, and chemical contamination.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I therefore request confirmation that the planned in=
spection and sampling will be expanded to include all levels and relevant s=
tructural areas. Alternatively, please confirm that Tower will meet my reas=
onable costs should I need to arrange
 independent specialists to carry out supplementary testing (including labo=
ratory analysis).<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Please confirm the final timing for the 17th and the=
 revised scope of testing once available.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Ng=C4=81 mihi,<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Raffaella<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
